longBusinessSummary: United Development Company Q.P.S.C., together with its subsidiaries, contributes and invests in infrastructure and utilities in the State of Qatar. It operates through four segments: Urban Development, Hospitality and Leisure, Infrastructure and Utilities, and Other Operations. The company is involved in the real estate development and construction activities; investment and development of hotel and leisure facilities; selling of luxurious items; and construction and management of district cooling systems and marina activities. It also engages in the urban development, environment related businesses, business management, and provision of information technology solutions. United Development Company Q.P.S.C. was incorporated in 1999 and is based in Doha, Qatar.
